text: Samajik Ekta Party (Social United Party), a political party in Haryana, India. The party's president is Nafe Singh Dahiya. Ahead of the 1999 state assembly elections, SEP had joined the Haryana Sarvjatiya Morcha (Haryana All Caste Front). ==References== Category:Political parties in Haryana Category:Political parties in India
title: Samajik Ekta Party
